
A field's values are stored in one of several data structures
    The data structure depends on the field's data type
Ensures efficient data access - e.g. searches
Handles by Apache Lucene, not ElasticSearch

***********************************************************************
Inverted indices
    . Mapping between terms and which document conatin them 
    . Outside the contect of analyzers, we use the terminology "terms"
    . Inverted indices exists within the scope of a field
    


